org.modelio.api.modelio.diagram

Interface IDiagramDrawing

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDiagramGraphic
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDiagramDrawingLink, IDiagramDrawingNode

    public interface IDiagramDrawing
extends IDiagramGraphic
    Diagram drawings are diagram graphics that are by nature not related to a model elements.

    IDiagramGraphic.getElement() will always return null for instances.

    Since:
    3.1
